s <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> official specs\n- Uses <span class=\"hljs-number\" class=\"hljs-number\">8</span>-dimension comparison framework\n- Validates <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">with</span> real-world scenarios\n- Outputs structured report <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">with</span> citations\n</code></pre></div></div><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"Key-Features\">Key Features</h2><p>Feature Description <strong>Source Tiering</strong> L1-L4 hierarchy ensures conclusion traceability <strong>Time-sensitivity</strong> Auto-detects fast-moving fields (AI, crypto, etc.) <strong>Fact Cards</strong> Every claim has source, confidence level, applicability <strong>Explicit Derivation</strong> No &quot;I feel like&quot; - only mechanism-based conclusions <strong>Deliverable Output</strong> One-line summary + structured chapters + citations</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"FAQ\">FAQ</h2><p><strong>Q: How is this different from just asking Claude to research something?</strong></p><p>A: This skill enforces a systematic methodology with intermediate artifacts, source verification, and explicit reasoning chains. Results are traceable and verifiable.</p><p><strong>Q: Does it work for non-technical topics?</strong></p><p>A: Yes, the methodology applies to any research topic. The 5 problem types (concept comparison, decision support, trend analysis, problem diagnosis, knowledge organization) cover most use cases.</p><p><strong>Q: How does it handle outdated information?</strong></p><p>A: Step 0.5 assesses time-sensitivity. For high-sensitivity fields (AI, blockchain), it enforces 6-month time windows and requires version number citations.</p><h1 level=\"1\" id=\"Deep-Research深度调研\">Deep Research（深度调研）</h1><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://bgithub.xyz/wshuyi/deep-research/blob/main/README.md\">English</a></p><p>一个 Claude Code 技能，通过系统化的 8 步方法论，将模糊主题转化为高质量、可交付的调研报告。</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"痛点\">痛点</h2><p>在调研复杂主题时，你经常面临：</p><ul><li><p><strong>信息过载</strong>：来源太多，难以区分质量</p></li><li><p><strong>结论模糊</strong>：「我感觉像 X」而非基于证据的推理</p></li><li><p><strong>无法追溯</strong>：不知道结论从何而来</p></li><li><p><strong>时效盲区</strong>：在 AI 等快速变化领域使用过时信息</p></li></ul><p>传统调研耗时长，结论往往不可靠。</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"解决方案\">解决方案</h2><p>Deep Research 提供<strong>系统化的 8 步方法论</strong>：</p><ul><li><p><strong>资料分层评估</strong>：L1（官方文档）&gt; L2（博客）&gt; L3（媒体）&gt; L4（社区）</p></li><li><p><strong>带出处的事实卡片</strong>：每条论断都可追溯到来源</p></li><li><p><strong>时效敏感性评估</strong>：自动处理快速变化的领域</p></li><li><p><strong>可验证的结论</strong>：「事实 → 对照 → 结论」显式推导链</p></li><li><p><strong>可交付的输出</strong>：老板能读、能转述、能追溯的报告</p></li></ul><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"环境要求\">环境要求</h2><ul><li><p>Claude Code CLI</p></li><li><p>网络搜索工具（WebSearch、Tavily MCP 或 Exa MCP）</p></li></ul><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"安装方式\">安装方式</h2><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"方式-1Git-Clone最简单\">方式 1：Git Clone（最简单）</h3><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code>git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/wshuyi/deep-research.git\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">cp</span> -r deep-research/skills/deep-research ~/.claude/skills/</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"方式-2插件市场\">方式 2：插件市场</h3><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code>/plugin marketplace add wshuyi/deep-research\n/plugin install deep-research@wshuyi/deep-research</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"方式-3第三方市场\">方式 3：第三方市场</h3><p>仓库获得 2+ stars 后会被 <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://skillsmp.com\">SkillsMP</a> 自动收录，可直接搜索「deep-research」安装。</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"使用方法\">使用方法</h2><p>自然语言触发：</p><ul><li><p>「深度调研 [主题]」</p></li><li><p>「帮我调研 [主题]」</p></li><li><p>「对比分析 X 和 Y」</p></li><li><p>「写调研报告」</p></li></ul><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"工作流程8-步法\">工作流程（8 步法）</h2><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">yaml</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 0:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">问题类型判断</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 0.5:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">时效敏感性评估（AI/技术类主题必须执行）</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 1:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">问题拆解与边界界定</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 2:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">资料分层与权威锁定</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 3:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">事实抽取与证据卡片</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 4:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">建立对比/分析框架</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 5:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">参照物基准对齐</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 6:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">从事实到结论的推导链</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 7:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">用例验证（Sanity</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">Check）</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">Step 8:</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">可交付化处理</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"输出结构\">输出结构</h2><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">ruby</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code>~<span class=\"hljs-regexp\" class=\"hljs-regexp\">/Downloads/research</span><span class=\"hljs-regexp\" class=\"hljs-regexp\">/&lt;topic&gt;/</span>\n├── 00_问题拆解.md          <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 问题类型、子问题列表</span>\n├── 01_资料来源.md          <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 所有资料链接和摘要</span>\n├── 02_事实卡片.md          <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 抽取的事实及出处</span>\n├── 03_对比框架.md          <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 选定的框架和填充</span>\n├── 04_推导过程.md          <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 事实→结论的推导</span>\n├── 05_验证记录.md          <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 用例验证和回查</span>\n└── <span class=\"hljs-variable,constant_\" class=\"hljs-variable,constant_\">FINAL_</span>调研报告.md       <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 最终交付报告</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"示例\">示例</h2><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">diff</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code>用户：深度调研 REST API 和 GraphQL 的区别\n\nClaude：[执行 8 步方法论]\n<span class=\"hljs-deletion\" class=\"hljs-deletion\">- 判断类型：概念对比型</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-deletion\" class=\"hljs-deletion\">- 从官方规范创建事实卡片</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-deletion\" class=\"hljs-deletion\">- 使用 8 维度对比框架</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-deletion\" class=\"hljs-deletion\">- 用实际场景验证</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-deletion\" class=\"hljs-deletion\">- 输出带引用的结构化报告</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"核心特性\">核心特性</h2><p>特性 说明 <strong>资料分层</strong> L1-L4 层级确保结论可追溯 <strong>时效敏感</strong> 自动检测快速变化领域（AI、加密货币等） <strong>事实卡片</strong> 每条事实都有来源、置信度、适用范围 <strong>显式推导</strong> 不说「我感觉像」，只有机制对比得出的结论 <strong>可交付输出</strong> 一句话总结 + 结构化章节 + 引用来源</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"常见问题\">常见问题</h2><p><strong>Q: 这和直接让 Claude 调研有什么区别？</strong></p><p>A: 本技能强制执行系统化方法论，有中间产物、来源验证、显式推理链。结果可追溯、可验证。</p><p><strong>Q: 非技术类主题也能用吗？</strong></p><p>A: 可以，方法论适用于任何调研主题。5 种问题类型（概念对比、决策支持、趋势分析、问题诊断、知识梳理）覆盖大多数场景。</p><p><strong>Q: 如何处理过时信息？</strong></p><p>A: Step 0.5 评估时效敏感性。对于高敏感领域（AI、区块链），强制执行 6 个月时间窗口，要求标注版本号。</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"许可证\">许可证</h2><p>MIT License - 详见 <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://bgithub.xyz/wshuyi/deep-research/blob/main/LICENSE\">LICENSE</a></p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"作者\">作者</h2><ul><li><p><strong>wshuyi</strong> - <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"https://bgithub.xyz/wshuyi\">GitHub</a></p></li></ul><script type=\"module\">const injectHtml = (root, html) => {\n  const iframe = document.createElement(\"iframe\");\n  const htmlContent = `<html><head></head><body>${html}</body></html>`;\n  iframe.style.width = \"100%\";\n  iframe.style.height = \"100%\";\n  iframe.onload = () => {\n    const doc = iframe.contentDocument || iframe.contentWindow?.document;\n    if (!doc) {\n      return;\n    }\n    doc.open();\n    doc.write(htmlContent);\n    doc.close();\n  };\n  root.replaceChildren(iframe);\n}\n  document.querySelectorAll('.playground')?.forEach(el=>{\n    const html = el.getAttribute('data-html');\n    if (html) {\n      injectHtml(el,html);\n    }\n    const indicator = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    indicator.className = \"indicator\";\n    const showCode = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    showCode.className = \"show-code\";\n    showCode.innerText = \"code\";\n    showCode.onclick = () => {\n      el.parentElement.classList.remove(\"preview-only\");\n    };\n    const showPreview = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    showPreview.className = \"show-preview\";\n    showPreview.innerText = \"preview\";\n    showPreview.onclick = () => {\n      el.parentElement.classList.add(\"preview-only\");\n    };\n    indicator.appendChild(showCode);\n    indicator.appendChild(showPreview);\n    el.parentElement.appendChild(indicator);\n    if (window.screen.width < 768) {\n      showPreview.click();\n    }\n  });</script>","id":"lllslsttssstttlll","path":"/posts/lllslsttssstttlll.json"}